1. Create folder wherever u want repository in your local machine

2. Through Git bash(windows) go to that created folder.

3. Enter command

  git clone repository url

4. Now u get server code into the local repository

5.update your code by simply replacing files in local repository

6. Enter command after following step 2.

  git add *

  git commit

  git pull (if anyone changed the code in repository)

  git push

7.U can directly follow from step 5 next time onwards.



note : when u commit code u will get vi editor or any other editor to write changes u made in the updated code.